{"tid":1641982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[死性不改]道地擺明唔驚你罷買 長期落CCTVB廣告！","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T08:44:34.000Z","uid":75759,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"d9514f9c349dc9543b0e070d03484aba368fe095","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係品牌負資產，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅品牌形象將付諸流水！無人可憐！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>TVB<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今個月</span></span>開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">年底</span></span>啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【點解搞道地？】</span><br />\n<br />\n自從我哋向道地提出對佢落CCTVB廣告嘅意見以嚟，<span style=\"color: gold;\">已經過了一個月有多</span>，然而我哋<span style=\"color: gold;\">仍然得唔到回應</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">道地嘅廣告亦繼續在匪趣台播放中</span>，默默支持編造假新聞嘅紅媒CCTVB為禍人間。<br />\n<br />\n作為#地道 嘅香港人，我哋一定要秉持「藍罷買 黃幫襯」嘅原則，支持清楚願意同香港人同行嘅良心企業，同時與「支持無線新聞 造假出賣港人」嘅公司劃清界線！對樓豬嚟講，道地一啲都唔地道，恥與為伍！<br />\n<br />\n正因為道地一直漠視我哋嘅訴求，激到心穎都回魂出黎呼籲大家抵制佢旗下其他品牌！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LYu78H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LYu78H.png&h=7677e3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWJfjjC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWJfjjC.png&h=0304d4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@9 Oct 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Meko(道地)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ilovemeko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Filovemeko&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=4cb8fa6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ilovemeko</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span>去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">※請善用template，清晰表達訴求</span></span><br />\n二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。 <br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QE2jK3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQE2jK3X.jpg&h=f254329f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WKaRKd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WKaRKd.gif&h=1b609e93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XW1dXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XW1dXA.png&h=64a47a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=4d959075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=742f23cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7a3413fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"15ef4a9e6c07dbee6776ab5e7198b936a3d95407","tid":1641982,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:57:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2941116caa2eafdd02a337be7211a41337bd3881","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f111a12beb1ed3bd0eb11f02f4684428a79c0a1d","tid":1641982,"uid":56472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a59522ee303ba1ca536a24eca9cd771eed9e1f8","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78ae1b7ca3c0174b5cd3cb115322ab6c88d34b5","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc28d736629e2c5132d2cbaf2157331f47e5553","tid":1641982,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581d91d4c644f7a3ac8180c5f217379ce175709b","tid":1641982,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7ed669463304f92e9e090c0fc7324a9932661d","tid":1641982,"uid":7612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:04:26.000Z","msg":"道地 劉華 收皮啦"},{"pid":"151a73fc351bb2df5758528e2cee90f6edc54b00","tid":1641982,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"咪再飲屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0feb4b9bb03e5733ff4cdf37f48e9a1223ea4454","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:07:32.000Z","msg":"道地不了<br />\n寧願行遠少少去百佳買其他茶飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c915e25e1f3cc52ccfe6d8aa5572204012f973","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">T</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">V</span><span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>開始要黨出手打救</strong></span>  <br />\n十月新廣告商全撚部都係中資：<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國近海石油<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />招商局集團 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />華潤集團 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國聯通  <br />\n除左華潤其他幾間同日常消費完全冇關，咁嘅時勢亦都冇必要仲喺TVB唱臭個名 <br />\n所以落廣告原因只有兩個 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 表忠 2. 救TVB</span></span> <br />\n要黨出手就證明TVB真係唔撚掂 <br />\n有廣告界手足表示下年已經少左30%廣告 大家俾啲力 再推盡佢！ <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viAhpCW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviAhpCW.jpg&h=c11150fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEPYTwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEPYTwh.jpg&h=31110a6a&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成日影手足大頭 宜家就有個最和理非最低成本嘅方法就可以加速TVB滅亡 宜家同我入黎做任 繼續洗版 洗到佢仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"eb9ea30f857ccac22635704af26097201819d1d8","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8b10e8ad3f00d5087e6b3a27a00ca230e7dfe4","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e25a6bf0eeac3bb5a5a843fb1b4eab93e8718e0","tid":1641982,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3c59701ea30e3029bde6a0f4a7e6625f37e85e","tid":1641982,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"543fc56e74e9ad710e611747f867d36e2044fb4a","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7e0efa6f318d147ab35255bed2e2921d5cda15","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxU98mf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxU98mf.png&h=70055f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaWXxNW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaWXxNW.png&h=b6b9b105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween<br />\n聽日全民購物日大家都要多多支持呀<br />\n黃店就係要用銀紙黎懲罰<br />\n道地就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bab9929a894039056133357d63052401092d1a9","tid":1641982,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"罷買，上facebook留言"},{"pid":"b285138f3efad4035f4fd859bf18edc65efe101b","tid":1641982,"uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"唔飲"},{"pid":"430dcc3631c240b1514ed7972c760022c7391372","tid":1641982,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae49d7514023fde0a245fc40f1259d6788c9c0c4","tid":1641982,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eef0e743a9cc55ae002f5e1ac560831ca861a26","tid":1641982,"uid":45934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"今次仆街了!<br />\n我飲開個支OATLY 都係Telford 代理<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.telford.com.hk/non_alcoholic/en/brandlist.php?cid=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telford.com.hk%2Fnon_alcoholic%2Fen%2Fbrandlist.php%3Fcid%3D7&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f5e9bf5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telford.com.hk/non_alcoholic/en/brandlist.php?cid=7</a><br />\nOATLY 有隻barista 版加咖啡度好好飲!<br />\nCHARBUCKS OAT LATTE 都係用佢<br />\n<br />\n三十幾蚊支我仲個個星期買<br />\n以後唔撚飲<br />\n#oatly"},{"pid":"d9065559e78387e8e4c2d756006e8a9d7effa741","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b324f018cb9a2457236efc9c0669307911b88b1","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">T</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">V</span><span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>開始要黨出手打救</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n十月新廣告商全撚部都係中資：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國近海石油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />招商局集團<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />華潤集團<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國聯通<br />\n<br />\n除左華潤其他幾間同日常消費完全冇關，咁嘅時勢亦都冇必要仲喺TVB唱臭個名<br />\n所以落廣告原因只有兩個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 表忠<br />\n2. 救TVB</span></span><br />\n要黨出手就證明TVB真係唔撚掂<br />\n有廣告界手足表示下年已經少左30%廣告<br />\n大家俾啲力 再推盡佢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viAhpCW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviAhpCW.jpg&h=c11150fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEPYTwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEPYTwh.jpg&h=31110a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日影手足大頭 宜家就有個最和理非最低成本嘅方法就可以加速TVB滅亡<br />\n宜家同我入黎做任<br />\n繼續洗版<br />\n洗到佢仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地贏緊 咪撚再話冇機會贏<br />\n我要士氣！！！"},{"pid":"a524e6ddf969451a3e1450dd923617a11a61208b","tid":1641982,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eef0e743a9cc55ae002f5e1ac560831ca861a26","tid":1641982,"uid":45934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"今次仆街了!<br />\n我飲開個支OATLY 都係Telford 代理<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.telford.com.hk/non_alcoholic/en/brandlist.php?cid=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telford.com.hk%2Fnon_alcoholic%2Fen%2Fbrandlist.php%3Fcid%3D7&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f5e9bf5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telford.com.hk/non_alcoholic/en/brandlist.php?cid=7</a><br />\nOATLY 有隻barista 版加咖啡度好好飲!<br />\nCHARBUCKS OAT LATTE 都係用佢<br />\n<br />\n三十幾蚊支我仲個個星期買<br />\n以後唔撚飲<br />\n#oatly"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"黃懲罰 藍罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab12ca8f0495cc64ee30b7f055ce719e2157423","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c2fa57aaf4721c8a53814ed07c7e13a7243e22","tid":1641982,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30b20a8dfc521cb5931765cc3c15410cc0ead4c9","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1eef0e743a9cc55ae002f5e1ac560831ca861a26","tid":1641982,"uid":45934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"今次仆街了!<br />\n我飲開個支OATLY 都係Telford 代理<br />\nli