e":"2019-10-09T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5b410170f22e2ae90187fcb75b0f90459402d0","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b8d8b70292b655ccf7c5a70bb160f629945a9b","tid":1641982,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b053aa0aa387d9719734af8eba7b28f2efb7bcae","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee299b79af40a6979b38655a1d8980bdb949762","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"雖然填海華冇做道地代言人好耐，但係諗起道地就會諗起佢。。。"},{"pid":"16d8883bb30fb9c2b06ad0883966ae6b9661c373","tid":1641982,"uid":326807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"事到如今<br />\n係咪應該要主動設死線 發比cctvb所有廣告商<br />\n<br />\n例如： 向所有廣告商發出最後通牒，11月中前 要明確咁表明完佐現有合約，之後會唔會再係cctvb落廣告。<br />\n<br />\n【恥與為伍】TVB 要佢死 就要夠狠毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642486</a>"},{"pid":"d257004a9f0bb981791c5fd6ec4044afd221c0f3","tid":1641982,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483327e5e8789de88979aa083729df60079b4f7b","tid":1641982,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:01